{"id": 2061, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得商家对健康食品都有什么误解？", "description": "宣称自己的产品很健康的时候，他们是怎么断章取义忽悠你的？（题图来自：GIPHY)", "record_count": 9275, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201712121430555ZwJyhurfGKxzXNB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-13T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3411, "title": "你觉得商家对健康食品都有什么误解？", "content": "你觉得商家对健康食品都有什么误解？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 253899, "content": "原汤即是胜利，猪骨汤胆固醇高健康不到哪里去", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143132WfCXsEigJLvlTo2h.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 253900, "content": "明星配料撑场面，只说凉茶败火，不说放了多少糖", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143204x0oRCwUMSbGYLQa2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 253901, "content": "强调相对健康，玉米片是比薯片强，但盐放很多钠超标", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143221BY5CnW8NQ9sySPTF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 253902, "content": "让食品添加剂背锅，但无添加不等于一定好", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143728UZhcjPCMGyLSfO8A.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 253903, "content": "忽略烹饪方式，蔬菜做成果蔬干后维生素和水已经流失", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143252Y94SOehBLIWDqEQA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 253904, "content": "蹭个别口味热度 ，紫薯/南瓜口味就代表降脂养生", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143312Qo9FRSTiW4j5e1Z2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 253905, "content": "只看卡路里，代餐热量低，但并不能均衡饮食结构", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143327GFxwvemETfCd1W4M.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 253906, "content": "假设补越多越好，但不是人人都缺钙缺维生素", "image": "img/option/option/20171212143655B6Ga3cHR8qfehKjQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}